{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.inferMatchType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">inferMatchType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a `MatcherApp`, replaces the motive with one that is inferred from the actual types of the\nalternatives.\n\nFor example, given\n```\n(match (motive := Nat → Unit → ?) n with\n 0 => 1\n _ => true) ()\n```\n(for any `?`; the motive’s result type be ignored) will give this type\n```\n(match n with\n | 0 => Nat\n | _ => Bool)\n```\n\nThe given `MatcherApp` must not use a splitter in `matcherName`.\nThe resulting expression *will* use the splitter corresponding to `matcherName` (this is necessary\nfor the construction).\n\nInternally, this needs to reduce the matcher in a given branch; this is done using\n`Split.simpMatchTarget`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.inferMatchType","kind":"def","line":434,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.inferMatchType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L434-L504"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.transform\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">transform</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#MonadLiftT\">MonadLiftT</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Control/Basic.html#MonadControlT\">MonadControlT</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Exception.html#Lean.MonadError\">MonadError</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.MonadEnv\">MonadEnv</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Log.html#Lean.MonadLog\">MonadLog</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.AddMessageContext\">AddMessageContext</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.MonadOptions\">MonadOptions</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">useSplitter </span><span class=\"fn\">addEqualities</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">onParams</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">onMotive</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></span></span> := <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>) (<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a> <span class=\"fn\">e</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">onAlt</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></span></span></span></span> :=\n  <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>) (<span class=\"fn\">x_1</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>) (<span class=\"fn\">x_2</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>) (<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a> <span class=\"fn\">e</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">onRemaining</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Performs a possibly type-changing transformation to a `MatcherApp`.\n\n* `onParams` is run on each parameter and discriminant\n* `onMotive` runs on the body of the motive, and is passed the motive parameters\n  (one for each `MatcherApp.discrs`)\n* `onAlt` runs on each alternative, and is passed the expected type of the alternative,\n   as inferred from the motive\n* `onRemaining` runs on the remaining arguments (and may change their number)\n\nIf `useSplitter` is true, the matcher is replaced with the splitter.\nNB: Not all operations on `MatcherApp` can handle one `matcherName` is a splitter.\n\nIf `addEqualities` is true, then equalities connecting the discriminant to the parameters of the\nalternative (like in `match h : x with …`) are be added, if not already there.\n\nThis function works even if the type of alternatives do *not* fit the inferred type. This\nallows you to post-process the `MatcherApp` with `MatcherApp.inferMatchType`, which will\ninfer a type, given all the alternatives.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.transform","kind":"def","line":245,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.transform","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L245-L430"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.all\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">all</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvars</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"All proper fvars in binding order, matching the lambdas that `transform` wraps around the alt result. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.all","kind":"def","line":241,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.all","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L241-L243"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.altParams\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">altParams</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvars</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `altParams` that were used for `instantiateLambda alt altParams` inside `transform`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.altParams","kind":"def","line":237,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.altParams","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L237-L239"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.extraEqs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">extraEqs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Extra equation fvars added by `addEqualities` (see `heq` in the example above). ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.extraEqs","kind":"def","line":235,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.extraEqs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L235-L235"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.discrEqs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">discrEqs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Discriminant equation fvars from the matcher's own type (`numDiscrEqs`). ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.discrEqs","kind":"def","line":233,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.discrEqs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L233-L233"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.overlaps\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">overlaps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Overlap parameter fvars (non-casesOn splitters only). ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.overlaps","kind":"def","line":231,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.overlaps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L231-L231"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.fields\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">fields</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Constructor field fvars, i.e. the proper fvar subset of `args` (see example above). ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.fields","kind":"def","line":229,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.fields","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L229-L229"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.args\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">args</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">TransformAltFVars</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Arguments for `instantiateLambda` on the original alternative (see example above).\nMay include non-fvar values like `Unit.unit` for thunked alternatives. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.args","kind":"def","line":227,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.args","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L227-L227"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> →\n  <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\">Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.mk","kind":"ctor","line":204,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L204-L235"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformAltFVars</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Fvars/exprs introduced in the telescope of a matcher alternative during `transform`.\n\n* `args` are the values passed to `instantiateLambda` on the original alt. They usually\n  coincide with `fields`, but may include non-fvar values (e.g. `Unit.unit` for thunked alts).\n* `fields` are the constructor-field fvars (proper fvar subset of `args`).\n* `overlaps` are overlap-parameter fvars (splitter path only, for non-`casesOn` splitters).\n* `discrEqs` are discriminant-equation fvars from the matcher's own type (`numDiscrEqs`).\n* `extraEqs` are equation fvars added by the `addEqualities` flag.\n\n**Example.** `transform` with `addEqualities := true` on a `Nat.casesOn` application\n`Nat.casesOn (motive := …) n alt₀ alt₁` opens alt telescopes:\n```\nAlt 0 (zero):  (heq : n = Nat.zero) → motive Nat.zero\n  ⟹ { args := #[], fields := #[], extraEqs := #[heq] }\n\nAlt 1 (succ):  (k : Nat) → (heq : n = Nat.succ k) → motive (Nat.succ k)\n  ⟹ { args := #[k], fields := #[k], extraEqs := #[heq] }\n```\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars","kind":"structure","line":204,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.TransformAltFVars","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L204-L235"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.withUserNames\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">withUserNames</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Control/Basic.html#MonadControlT\">MonadControlT</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvars</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">names</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Sets the user name of the FVars in the local context according to the given array of names.\n\nIf they differ in size the shorter size wins.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.withUserNames","kind":"def","line":182,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.withUserNames","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L182-L189"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">refineThrough?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A non-failing version of `MatcherApp.refineThrough` ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough?","kind":"def","line":168,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L168-L174"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">refineThrough</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given\n- matcherApp `match_i As (fun xs => motive[xs]) discrs (fun ys_1 => (alt_1 : motive (C_1[ys_1])) ... (fun ys_n => (alt_n : motive (C_n[ys_n]) remaining`, and\n- a expression `B[discrs]` (which may not be a type, e.g. `n : Nat`),\nreturns the expressions `fun ys_1 ... ys_i => B[C_1[ys_1]] ... B[C_n[ys_n]]`,\n\nThis method assumes\n- the `matcherApp.motive` is a lambda abstraction where `xs.size == discrs.size`\n- each alternative is a lambda abstraction where `ys_i.size == matcherApp.altNumParams[i]`\n\nThis is similar to `MatcherApp.addArg` when you only have an expression to\nrefined, and not a type with a value.\n\nThis is used in `Lean.Elab.PreDefinition.WF.GuessFix` when constructing the context of recursive\ncalls to refine the functions' parameter, which may mention `major`.\nSee there for how to use this function.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough","kind":"def","line":114,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.refineThrough","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L114-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">addArg?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Similar to `MatcherApp.addArg`, but returns `none` on failure. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg?","kind":"def","line":106,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L106-L111"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">MatcherApp</span>.<span class=\"name\">addArg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">matcherApp</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp\">MatcherApp</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given\n- matcherApp `match_i As (fun xs => motive[xs]) discrs (fun ys_1 => (alt_1 : motive (C_1[ys_1])) ... (fun ys_n => (alt_n : motive (C_n[ys_n]) remaining`, and\n- expression `e : B[discrs]`,\nConstruct the term\n`match_i As (fun xs => B[xs] -> motive[xs]) discrs (fun ys_1 (y : B[C_1[ys_1]]) => alt_1) ... (fun ys_n (y : B[C_n[ys_n]]) => alt_n) e remaining`.\n\nWe only abstract discriminants that are fvars.  We used to use `kabstract` to abstract all\ndiscriminants from `B[discrs]`, but that changes the type of the arg in ways that make it no\nlonger compatible with the original recursive function (issue #7322).\n\nIf this is still not great, then we could try to use `kabstract`, but only on the last parameter\nof the `arg` (the termination proof obligation).\n\nThis method assumes\n- the `matcherApp.motive` is a lambda abstraction where `xs.size == discrs.size`\n- each alternative is a lambda abstraction where `ys_i.size == matcherApp.altNumParams[i]`\n\nThis is used in `Lean.Elab.PreDefinition.WF.Fix` when replacing recursive calls with calls to\nthe argument provided by `fix` to refine type of the local variable used for recursive calls,\nwhich may mention `major`. See there for how to use this function.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.html#Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"Lean.Meta.MatcherApp.addArg","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Match/MatcherApp/Transform.lean#L48-L104"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.AppBuilder","Lean.Meta.Match.AltTelescopes","Lean.Meta.Match.MatchEqsExt","Lean.Meta.Match.MatcherApp.Basic","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Refl","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Split"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Match.MatcherApp.Transform"}